headline: Freshworks Inc. (FRSH) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Freshworks (FRSH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +50.00% and +2.99%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
